Welcome to the TOEFL code 'INNTO'
Type make to install the documentation and open with
    firefox doc/html/index.html

To install the code you need to have fftw3, OpenGl and 
glfw (http://www.glfw.org/download.html) 
installed in standard locations. 
Then go to the source directory and type make. 
In the lib directory type make toefl to see a test program running the
rayleigh-benard convection code. 




